<paragraph blockId="7.[178,1085,502,580]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1126">
Distribution and natural history: The type locality is situated to the west of Telavi in eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[476,561,530,552]" name="Georgia" pageId="7" pageNumber="1126">Georgia</collectingCountry>
. The 
<typeStatus box="[618,706,530,552]" pageId="7" pageNumber="1126">holotype</typeStatus>
was sifted from leaf litter in a beech forest at an altitude of approximately 
<quantity box="[560,639,558,579]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.09" pageId="7" pageNumber="1126" unit="m" value="1090.0">1090 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
